headline: Janus Henderson U.S. Real Estate ETF Q4 2024 Commentary
summary: The Fund returned -6.46% and the FTSE Nareit Equity REITs Index returned -6.21%. Wyndham Hotels & Resorts and Equinix contributed positively, while Lineage and Public Storage detracted.
